证据片段: The matrix composition in one Zircaloy-2 (Zry-2) and four Zircaloy-4 (Zry-4) materials has been measured with the atom probe technique.

文献ID: STP1132-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_9th Volume_030_chunk1
证据片段: No significant difference in matrix concentration of Fe and Cr could be detected in Zry-4 materials with different heat treatment and different corrosion resistance.

证据片段: Transmission electron microscopy of the oxide layers showed that these were approximately 10 nm thick and contained 5 nm sized oxide crystallites in an amorphous layer.

证据片段: According to atom probe analysis, the thin oxide layers had a low oxygen content, less than 50 atomic percent.

证据片段: Charquet et al. [10] have thoroughly examined the separate and combined solubility of Fe and Cr in the α-phase of alloys resembling the Zircaloys. They found that the highest combined solubility of Fe + Cr was 150 weight ppm at 810°C in a Zry-1.4Sn alloy with a Fe-to-Cr ratio similar to that in Zry-4.
